<taxonomicName id="4C2877CF0846FFE098D7FC113078FC4C" authorityName="Esyunin" authorityYear="1992" box="[391,555,975,1001]" class="Arachnida" family="Linyphiidae" genus="Uralophantes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="6" pageNumber="27" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="troitskensis">
<emphasis id="B95CD05E0846FFE098D7FC113078FC4C" box="[391,555,975,1001]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="27">U. troitskensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
not representing a case of intraspecific variability of the last one.
</paragraph>
